    {
      "_id": "MPParagraphElement:E455831D-1327-44E9-8B73-619AD819F59D",
      "contents": "<p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"MPParagraphElement:E455831D-1327-44E9-8B73-619AD819F59D\" class=\"MPElement\" data-object-type=\"MPParagraphElement\">At the start of this project, 610 papers were gathered from different sources, and 423 were chosen for the survey. More than 90% of these articles were published between 2010 and 2021. Therefore, we used more recent articles to update this review.</p>",
