      "contents": "<p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"MPParagraphElement:C86C97C9-C50B-447F-ABBF-D404F2891403\" class=\"MPElement\" data-object-type=\"MPParagraphElement\">Table <span class=\"cross-reference\" data-reference-id=\"MPAuxiliaryObjectReference:98D758FB-014C-4FA1-901D-D155D75C2F43\"><span class=\"kind elementIndex\"><b>7</b></span></span> shows the pros and cons of segmentation methods.</p>",
