    {
      "_id": "MPParagraphElement:086B81B6-6BF2-4201-9D4F-413F933A988D",
      "contents": "<p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"MPParagraphElement:086B81B6-6BF2-4201-9D4F-413F933A988D\" class=\"MPElement\" data-object-type=\"MPParagraphElement\">Lung cancer detection techniques are improving day by day. Currently, available lung cancer detection techniques are quite good in terms of performance, but there are many more limitations that researchers have encountered. Many issues have been resolved, but some remain.</p>",
      "createdAt": 1694167156,
      "updatedAt": 1694167156,
